OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1782915514
OL,3,CSeabird numbers soar on Lundy Island
OL,4,C20 years after rats eradicated
OL,6,FThe number of puffins and other
OL,7,Fseabirds on Lundy Island in the
OL,8,FBristol Channel has soared since it
OL,9,Fwas declared "rat-free" 20 years ago.
OL,11,FEfforts to clear the island of
OL,12,Finvasive rats, which prey on birds,
OL,13,Feggs and chicks, were officially
OL,14,Fdeclared a success in March 2006.
OL,26,@qD@NOUqD@WO]
