FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1782915514
OL,3,CSeabird numbers soar on Lundy Island
OL,4,C20 years after rats eradicated
OL,6,FPuffins have recovered from the brink
OL,7,Fof extinction, with numbers increasing
OL,8,Ffrom just 13 birds on the island in
OL,9,F2000 before the eradication programme
OL,10,Fbegan to 1,335 individuals now.
OL,12,FHelen Booker, a Senior Conservation
OL,13,FOfficer with the RSPB, told ITV News
OL,14,FWest Country: "The impact of removing
OL,15,Frats on Lundy has been incredible, we
OL,16,Fwere particularly wanting to restore
OL,17,Fpopulations of Manx shearwaters and
OL,18,FPuffins if possible because both those
OL,19,Fbirds nest in burrows and they are
OL,20,Freally vulnerable to rats.
OL,26,@vD@OOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1782915514
OL,3,CSeabird numbers soar on Lundy Island
OL,4,C20 years after rats eradicated
OL,6,F"They are not evolved to be safe from
OL,7,Frats, they're evolved to be safe from
OL,8,FGreat Back Black Gulls, so removing
OL,9,Fthe rats who eat the eggs and chicks
OL,10,Fhas had a massive impact.
OL,12,F"We've seen numbers of Manx
OL,13,Fshearwaters increase from 300 breeding
OL,14,Fpairs back in 2001 to now 12,500
OL,15,Fbreeding pairs which is incredible.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1782915514
OL,3,CSeabird numbers soar on Lundy Island
OL,4,C20 years after rats eradicated
OL,6,F"The results have been beyond what we
OL,7,Fever expected, we were hoping to see
OL,8,Fpositive results because we knew we
OL,9,Fwere removing a real threat to those
OL,10,Fbirds but the increase has been beyond
OL,11,Fwhat we expected.
OL,13,F"For Puffins as well it's incredible,
OL,14,Fthe birds had almost gone from the
OL,15,Fisland, we were down to the last few
OL,16,Findividuals and there's now well over
OL,17,F1,000 so it's really exciting."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/15
