OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1782915514
OL,3,CSeabird numbers soar on Lundy Island
OL,4,C20 years after rats eradicated
OL,6,FMost people who visit the island go
OL,7,Fpurely to look at the birds and Ms
OL,8,FBooker added: "It's now possible to
OL,9,Fsee these birds in their glory. 20
OL,10,Fyears ago we were looking at just a
OL,11,Fremnant of the population, now you can
OL,12,Fsee them in good numbers and you can
OL,13,Fsee Puffins much more easily than it
OL,14,Fused to be which is fantastic for
OL,15,Fvisitors.
OL,17,F"It shows that when you remove rats,
OL,18,Fwhich we know are a problem for
OL,19,Fseabirds, this can have really
OL,20,Ffantastic results and it paves the way
OL,21,Ffor this happening on other islands.
OL,26,@pD@OOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
