OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1782915514
OL,3,CSeabird numbers soar on Lundy Island
OL,4,C20 years after rats eradicated
OL,6,F"It's really important we make our
OL,7,Fseabird islands more resilient. We've
OL,8,Fseen impacts of avian flu, we've seen
OL,9,Fbig winter storms which have big
OL,10,Fimpacts on adult seabirds and high
OL,11,Fmortality.
OL,13,F"So if we can make our seabird
OL,14,Fcolonies as resilient as possible then
OL,15,Fthey will better withstand these
OL,16,Fimpacts in the future."
OL,18,FSpecies that had seemed entirely lost
OL,19,Fto predation by rats on the island
OL,20,Fhave returned, the conservationists
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@WO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
