FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1782915514
OL,3,CSeabird numbers soar on Lundy Island
OL,4,C20 years after rats eradicated
OL,6,FThe first breeding storm petrels were
OL,7,Fconfirmed in 2014, having seemingly
OL,8,Fbeen absent since the 1930s, and there
OL,9,Fare now more than 150 pairs nesting on
OL,10,Fthe island.
OL,12,FIt is a remarkable turnaround for
OL,13,FLundy Island, owned by the National
OL,14,FTrust and managed by the Landmark
OL,15,FTrust, after it had previously seen
OL,16,Fseabird numbers plummet from an
OL,17,Festimated 80,000 in 1939 to just 7,351
OL,18,Fin a survey in 2000.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1782915514
OL,3,CSeabird numbers soar on Lundy Island
OL,4,C20 years after rats eradicated
OL,6,FA partnership between the RSPB,
OL,7,FNatural England, the National Trust
OL,8,Fand the Landmark Trust was formed in
OL,9,F2002 to deal with rats which were
OL,10,Fidentified as the primary threat to
OL,11,Fburrownesting birds such as Manx
OL,12,Fshearwaters and puffins. The rats had
OL,13,Fbeen inadvertently introduced via
OL,14,Fships and shipwrecks.
OL,16,FThe island was declared rat-free four
OL,17,Fyears later, and ongoing biosecurity
OL,18,Fand long-term monitoring have ensured
OL,19,Fit has stayed that way.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1782915514
OL,3,CSeabird numbers soar on Lundy Island
OL,4,C20 years after rats eradicated
OL,6,FAndrea Ayres from Natural England
OL,7,Fsaid: "This is a really inspirational
OL,8,Fproject, Natural England has been
OL,9,Finvolved by advising and supporting
OL,10,Fand working with our partners.
OL,12,F"The key successes have been through
OL,13,Flong term monitoring, through evidence
OL,14,Fled conservation and from that
OL,15,Fpartnership approach with all the
OL,16,Fpeople involved.
OL,18,F"There's more work to do and the team
OL,19,Fon Lundy are really on that.
OL,26,@oD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1782915514
OL,3,CSeabird numbers soar on Lundy Island
OL,4,C20 years after rats eradicated
OL,6,F"For me it's a fantastic nature story
OL,7,Fbut it's also a people story, so
OL,8,Fhaving visited the island last week it
OL,9,Fwas amazing to see families, school
OL,10,Fgroups, individuals really learning
OL,11,Fabout the birds that are there with a
OL,12,Fhuge group of volunteers that are
OL,13,Fexcited and enthusing people."
OL,15,FDerek Green, Lundy's managing
OL,16,Fdirector, said: "The remarkable
OL,17,Frecovery of Lundy's seabirds following
OL,18,Fthe successful rat eradication is one
OL,19,Fof the UK's great conservation success
OL,20,Fstories."
OL,26,@xD@QOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1782915514
OL,3,CSeabird numbers soar on Lundy Island
OL,4,C20 years after rats eradicated
OL,6,FHe said it showed how targeted
OL,7,Fconservation could restore entire
OL,8,Fecosystems, and said the thriving
OL,9,Fwildlife was now attracting more
OL,10,Fvisitors than ever before, supporting
OL,11,Flocal businesses and inspiring new
OL,12,Fgenerations of conservationists.
OL,14,FBen McCarthy, head of nature
OL,15,Fconservation at the National Trust,
OL,16,Fsaid: "Eradicating rats from the
OL,17,Fisland was a remarkable achievement
OL,18,Fmade possible through strong
OL,19,Fpartnership working and bold,
OL,20,Fambitious thinking.
OL,26,@xD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1782915514
OL,3,CSeabird numbers soar on Lundy Island
OL,4,C20 years after rats eradicated
OL,6,F"The Island's ongoing commitment to
OL,7,Fbiosecurity has helped keep the island
OL,8,Frat-free, and the results for seabirds
OL,9,Fhave been truly astonishing."
OL,11,FHe added: "The project is a powerful
OL,12,Freminder of how quickly nature can
OL,13,Frecover given the right conditions and
OL,14,Fthe space to thrive."
OL,16,FNow the RSPB is calling for greater
OL,17,Fprotection for the seas around the
OL,18,Fisland to safeguard the birds.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@]O]sD@KOUvD@UO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
