OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1782915514
OL,3,CSeabird numbers soar on Lundy Island
OL,4,C20 years after rats eradicated
OL,6,FHelen Booker added: "If restoring over
OL,7,F40,000 seabirds on a single island is
OL,8,Fachievable, just imagine what could be
OL,9,Fdone for nature across the UK if we
OL,10,Fscaled up this ambition.
OL,12,F"While Lundy itself has some
OL,13,Fprotection, the island and the waters
OL,14,Fthat its seabirds use remain highly
OL,15,Fvulnerable, as they are not considered
OL,16,Fwhen significant potential impacts are
OL,17,Fassessed.
OL,26,@nD@UOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1782915514
OL,3,CSeabird numbers soar on Lundy Island
OL,4,C20 years after rats eradicated
OL,6,F"These remarkable results reinforce
OL,7,Fthe need for Lundy to be designated as
OL,8,Fa Special Protection Area to safeguard
OL,9,Fseabirds at sea as well as on land."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@dO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/15
